<p>The following is a history of <a href="Liverpool_F.C." title="Liverpool F.C.">Liverpool F.C.</a>.</p>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG/300px-Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG" width="300" height="117" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG/450px-Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG/600px-Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Liverpool_F.C._League_Progress_1893-2012.PNG" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf8/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
