<div style="position:absolute;text-align:center;left:71px;top:174px"><a href="Kevin_Keegan" title="Kevin Keegan"><span style="color:White; font-size:87%;"><b>Keegan</b><br /></span></a></div>
<div style="position:absolute;text-align:center;left:64px;top:156.5px"><a href="Steve_Heighway" title="Steve Heighway"><span style="color:White; font-size:87%;"><b>Heighway</b><br /></span></a></div>
