<div style="position:absolute;text-align:center;left:127px;top:62px"><a href="Jamie_Carragher" title="Jamie Carragher"><span style="color:Maroon; font-size:87%;"><b>Carragher</b><br /></span></a></div>
<div style="position:absolute;text-align:center;left:11.5px;top:118px"><a href="Danny_Murphy_(footballer_born_1977)" title="Danny Murphy (footballer born 1977)"><span style="color:Navy; font-size:87%;"><b>Murphy</b><br /></span></a></div>
